Yeast life-span extension by calorie restriction is independent of NAD 
fluctuation.

Anderson RM(#)(1), Latorre-Esteves M(#)(1), Neves AR(2), Lavu S(1)(3), Medvedik 
O(1), Taylor C(3), Howitz KT(3), Santos H(2), Sinclair DA(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Pathology, Harvard Medical School, 200 Longwood Avenue, Boston 
